About This Company
The Wazzan group of companies has a rich and successful history since its inception more than 60 years ago.
The Group is active in various business streams such as Healthcare, Construction, Education, Electronics distribution and retail, investment, Real Estate and journalism.
Around 3,000 talented employees work for the Group from more than 30 nationalities.
The Headquarters is based in Kuwait and the Group currently operates in four countries; Kuwait, Qatar, Saudi Arabia and Egypt.
We look for people who can make a difference, add value, believe in our values and work as a part of our valuable and committed team. Morals, values and ethics are always at the core of our business.Our Subsidiaries are :Healthcare:•	NewMowasat Hospital Retail :•	Electrozan•	Supplying store Co. Education:•	The Gulf English School has an English curriculum.•	A’Takamul is English/ American, with an emphasis on the culture of Kuwait.•	Andalous and Tafawiq are large private Arabic schools. Constructions:•	Burhan International.•	Mushrif Trading & Contracting Company . •	Al Sabriya Electrical Co (Represents KONE, Finland).
